Have you ever wondered what J.K Rowling's magical world would be like if it was predominantly populated with melanin-rich people?  The Twitterverse seems to have a good idea with the #BlackHogwarts trending on Thursday night with many Harry Potter fans giving suggests of professors, which outfit they would wear after being sorted into a house and how certain events would've been different.  READ: J.K. Rowling defends Johnny Depp casting in 'Fantastic Beasts' Among some of the funnier suggestions included a class by Annalise Keating called "How To Get Away With Magic", having Snoop Dogg teach Herbology and having RuPaul's Drag Race host RuPaul Charles be the professor for the second years of advanced transfiguration.  